  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>On a successful deadly shot, you aim for the target&#8217;s eyes, seeking to take away their vision. The first time you hit a target while using this ability, they are dazzled for 1d4 rounds; if you successfully use this ability against a target already suffering from the dazzled condition, they are instead blinded for 1 minute. The blind condition can be removed with a DC 20 Heal check, or when the target receives at least 1 hit point of healing. If your base attack bonus is +10 or higher, you may use the blinding option of this ability even if the target is not dazzled.</p>\n",
